8. ⚠️ Risk Mitigation

Risk Probability Severity Mitigation Strategy
Contraction proof fails Medium High Fallback to Input-to-State Stability (ISS); prove bounded errors instead of exponential convergence
Graph ODE unstable in training High Medium Use neural ODE adjoint with gradient clipping; initialize near identity
CBF too conservative Medium Medium Learn CBF h(x) via reinforcement learning while maintaining feasibility constraints
Real-time latency too high Medium High Teacher-student distillation: train small policy from full CDIA; deploy student at 1kHz
Sim-to-real gap High Medium Domain randomization in Isaac Gym; system identification on real robot
Hardware failures Low High Digital twin validation; extensive simulation before real trials

